4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence that aims to provide professionals with the knowledge and skills to leverage AI in their current roles. This 6-week program covers various aspects of AI, including generative AI, context, prompts, and models. The course is designed to help participants strategically implement AI and enhance their workplace capabilities. It consists of 2 live, online classes per week with a maximum class size of 12 people. At the end of the course, participants receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required to enroll in this course. For more information, visit the website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course. stop